Now all I do is wait

09:03.777 --> 09:07.045
while I sit
on top of the crate
for safekeeping.

09:07.047 --> 09:10.048
(CHUPACABRA SCREECHING)
Hold that thought.
Mom will be back soon.

09:10.050 --> 09:13.718
Ha! How convenient
that your mother has a
whole tureen of goat biryani.

09:13.720 --> 09:15.453
